friend class NEWinogradLayerKernel
friend

Create a new Winograd convolution layer.

Parameters
[in]n_batchesNumber of batches in the input and output tensors.
[in]n_input_channelsNumber of feature maps in a batch of the input tensor.
[in]n_input_rowsNumber of rows in a feature map of the input tensor.
[in]n_input_colsNumber of columns in a feature map of the input tensor.
[in]n_output_channelsNumber of feature maps in the output tensor.
[in]same_paddingUse "SAME" padding, otherwise use "VALID".
[in]weightsPointer to weight tensor in spatial domain. Must be ordered as "Height x Rows x Input Feature Maps x Output Feature Maps.
[out]weights_storagePointer to storage for weight tensor in the Winograd domain. Must be at least the size returned by `get_weight_storage_size
[in]inputPointer to NHWC ordered input tensor, in the spatial domain.
[out]winograd_inputPointer to working space for the input tensor in the Winograd domain. Must be at least the size returned by get_input_storage_size.
[out]outputPointer to NHWC ordered output tensor, in the spatial domain.
[out]winograd_outputPointer to working space for the output tensor in the Winograd domain. Must be at least the size returned by get_output_storage_size.
